## Deploy Templates

Location: `templates\` folder. Naming: `<SiteName>_<InstallSource>.deploy.json`

Key fields: `SiteName`, `PhysicalPath`, `AppType`, `DotNetDll`, `InstallSource`, `InstallAppName`, `VirtualPath`, `ParentSite`, `HealthEndpoint`, `ApiPort`

- `InstallAppName` = folder name under `\\server\DedgeCommon\Software\DedgeWinApps\`
- `PhysicalPath` = local install path after `Install-OurWinApp` copies from staging
- For multi-project solutions: `InstallAppName` has component suffix (e.g. `GenericLogHandler-WebApi`), `SiteName` uses solution name only

