## Auth Flow (DedgeAuth connects all apps)

All consumer apps reference `DedgeAuth.Client` and use its middleware. DedgeAuth handles login, JWT tokens, session validation, tenant branding, user menus, and visit tracking. Consumer apps never implement their own auth — they delegate to DedgeAuth via `AddDedgeAuth()` + `UseDedgeAuth()` + `MapDedgeAuthProxy()`.
